t;/Producer(GPL Ghostscript SVN PRE-RELEASE 8.62)&#xA;/CreationDate(D:20080201212902-05&#39;00&#39;)&#xA;/ModDate(D:20080201212902-05&#39;00&#39;)&gt;&gt;endobj&#xA;xref&#xA;0 43&#xA;0000000000 65535 f &#xA;0000031564 00000 n &#xA;0000032497 00000 n &#xA;0000031456 00000 n &#xA;0000030334 00000 n &#xA;0000000015 00000 n &#xA;0000004837 00000 n &#xA;0000031940 00000 n &#xA;0000032147 00000 n &#xA;0000032357 00000 n &#xA;0000032079 00000 n &#xA;0000031612 00000 n &#xA;0000030476 00000 n &#xA;0000004857 00000 n &#xA;0000011364 00000 n &#xA;0000031671 00000 n &#xA;0000030620 00000 n &#xA;0000011385 00000 n &#xA;0000017164 00000 n &#xA;0000031712 00000 n &#xA;0000030764 00000 n &#xA;0000017185 00000 n &#xA;0000019816 00000 n &#xA;0000031762 00000 n &#xA;0000030908 00000 n &#xA;0000019837 00000 n &#xA;0000022318 00000 n &#xA;0000032218 00000 n &#xA;0000031812 00000 n &#xA;0000031052 00000 n &#xA;0000022339 00000 n &#xA;0000023854 00000 n &#xA;0000031862 00000 n &#xA;0000031196 00000 n &#xA;0000023875 00000 n &#xA;0000024215 00000 n &#xA;0000031901 00000 n &#xA;0000031340 00000 n &#xA;0000024235 00000 n &#xA;0000030313 00000 n &#xA;0000032021 00000 n &#xA;0000032299 00000 n &#xA;0000032439 00000 n &#xA;trailer&#xA;&lt;&lt; /Size 43 /Root 1 0 R /Info 2 0 R&#xA;/ID [&lt;F146DD6DF2A9059F740E1EFC01667AB8&gt;&lt;F146DD6DF2A9059F740E1EFC01667AB8&gt;]&#xA;&gt;&gt;&#xA;startxref&#xA;32636&#xA;%%EOF&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div&gt;Lobsters:&lt;div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;story_content&#34;&gt; &lt;div class=&#34;story_text&#34;&gt; &lt;p&gt;The traceroute utility on any computer connected to the Internet can be used to record the roundtrip time for small Internet packets between major Internet traffic hubs. Some of the routes include transmission over transoceanic fiber optic cable. We report on traceroute’s use by students to quickly and easily estimate the size of the earth. This is an inexpensive and quick way to involve introductory physics students in a hands−on use of scientific notation and to teach them about systematics in data.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
